<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:w="urn:import:fr.putnami.pwt.core.widget.client"
	xmlns:c="urn:import:fr.putnami.pwt.plugin.code.client">

	<ui:import field="fr.putnami.pwt.plugin.code.client.configuration.xml.XmlConfiguration.XML_CONFIGURATION" />

	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<w:Heading level="2" summary="docSummary">Panel</w:Heading>
		<p>
			A <code>Panel</code> is a widget with a header, a body and a footer. It uses the Header and Footer from his children.
		</p>
					
		<div class="showcase-sample-block">
			<div class="showcase-sample">
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Header>
						<w:Heading level="3">Panel content Header</w:Heading>
					</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>
						<w:Text>Panel content Footer</w:Text>
					</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Header>Panel content Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without footer</w:HTMLPanel>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without header</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel content Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without header nor footer</w:HTMLPanel>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Header>Panel without Content Header</w:Header>
					<w:Footer>Panel without Content Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Header>Panel without Content nor Footer Header</w:Header>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Footer>Panel without Content nor Header Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel>
					<w:Form>
						<w:Header>Form header</w:Header>
						<w:HTMLPanel>
							<p>Form Content</p>
						</w:HTMLPanel>
						<w:Footer>Form Footer</w:Footer>
					</w:Form>
				</w:Panel>
			</div>
			<c:StaticCode configuration="{XML_CONFIGURATION}">
<pre><![CDATA[
<w:Panel>
	<w:Header>
		<w:Heading level="3">Panel content Header</w:Heading>
	</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>
		<w:Text>Panel content Footer</w:Text>
	</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:Header>Panel content Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without footer</w:HTMLPanel>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without header</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel content Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:HTMLPanel>Panel Content without header nor footer</w:HTMLPanel>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:Header>Panel without Content Header</w:Header>
	<w:Footer>Panel without Content Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:Header>Panel without Content nor Footer Header</w:Header>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:Footer>Panel without Content nor Header Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel>
	<w:Form>
		<w:Header>Form header</w:Header>
		<w:HTMLPanel>
			<p>Form Content</p>
		</w:HTMLPanel>
		<w:Footer>Form Footer</w:Footer>
	</w:Form>
</w:Panel>]]></pre>
			</c:StaticCode>
		</div>
		
		<w:Heading level="3" summary="docSummary">Customization</w:Heading>
		<p>Use the <code>color</code> property to customize the panel.</p>
		<div class="showcase-sample-block">
			<div class="showcase-sample">
				<w:Panel color="PRIMARY">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel color="SUCCESS">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel color="INFO">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel color="WARNING">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel color="DANGER">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
			</div>
			<c:StaticCode configuration="{XML_CONFIGURATION}">
<pre><![CDATA[
<w:Panel color="PRIMARY">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel color="SUCCESS">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel color="INFO">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel color="WARNING">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel color="DANGER">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>]]></pre>
			</c:StaticCode>
		</div>
		
		<w:Heading level="3" summary="docSummary">Panel collapse</w:Heading>
		<p>Use the <code>collapsible</code> property to allow the panel to be collapsed, and set the <code>collapse</code> property to initialy collapse the panel.</p>
		<div class="showcase-sample-block">
			<div class="showcase-sample">
				<w:Panel collapsible="true">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel collapsible="true" collapse="true">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
				<w:Panel collapsible="true" collapse="false">
					<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
					<w:HTMLPanel>
						<p>Panel Content</p>
					</w:HTMLPanel>
					<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
				</w:Panel>
			</div>
			<c:StaticCode configuration="{XML_CONFIGURATION}">
<pre><![CDATA[
<w:Panel collapsible="true">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel collapsible="true" collapse="true">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>
<w:Panel collapsible="true" collapse="false">
	<w:Header>Panel Header</w:Header>
	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<p>Panel Content</p>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
	<w:Footer>Panel Footer</w:Footer>
</w:Panel>]]></pre>
			</c:StaticCode>
		</div>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder>